reviewText: The video dubbed the same interview as volume 1. Wanted more instruction. No doubt these guys are good but video is too short for the price.
Outstanding info for my agency training!

This DVD has good concepts.  I you're a Pro, maybe you won't need to buy this DVD, but if you're a begginer or just trying to improve your self defense technique (my case), its a good DVD.  I recommend it.
In comparison to its price, the information is too basic and too little.. Please avoid buying if you already know basics of martial arts.
